{"updated_at": "2012-02-09T01:43:49Z", "repo": "rails", "created_at": "2012-02-09T01:43:49Z", "owner": "rails", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/3880369", "id": 3880369, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/4918", "issue_id": 4918, "user": {"repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/pheld/repos", "type": "User", "html_url": "https://github.com/pheld", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/pheld/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/pheld/subscriptions", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/pheld/following{/other_user}", "gravatar_id": "ddc31dc6fa759854f475dccc87441b96", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/pheld/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/pheld", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/pheld/gists{/gist_id}", "avatar_url": "https://0.gravatar.com/avatar/ddc31dc6fa759854f475dccc87441b96?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F00efe3d30e8d51ae61fa5d5c96478a95.png", "id": 46692, "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/pheld/events{/privacy}", "login": "pheld", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/pheld/received_events", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/pheld/followers"}, "body": "Here's a freedom patch that works for this for now:\r\n\r\n```ruby\r\n  class << Mime::Type\r\n    Q_SEPARATOR_REGEXP = /;\\s*q=/\r\n\r\n    def parse_with_q_fix(accept_header)\r\n      if accept_header !~ /,/\r\n        accept_header = accept_header.split(Q_SEPARATOR_REGEXP).first\r\n      end\r\n\r\n      parse_without_q_fix accept_header\r\n    end\r\n\r\n    alias_method_chain :parse, :q_fix\r\n  end\r\n```", "_id": {"$oid": "52381f41bd3543c15100e74e"}, "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/4918#issuecomment-3880369"}
